flowchart TD
    A[Start Call] --> B{Is it a one-to-one or group call?}
    B -->|One-to-One| C[Establish Connection]
    B -->|Group Call| D[Create Conference Room]
    C --> E[Initiate Call Controls]
    D --> E
    E --> F{Is Quality Adequate?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Continue Call]
    F -->|No| H[Adapt Quality]
    H --> F
    G --> I[End Call]
    I --> J[Disconnect]